      public void onCommand​(net.dv8tion.jda.api.entities.User user, net.dv8tion.jda.api.entities.Guild guild, net.dv8tion.jda.api.entities.MessageChannel channel, net.dv8tion.jda.api.entities.Message message)
      A command which calculates a "love percentage" based on two strings. The input will be of the form "!lovecalc string0; string1". The strings chars will be turned into integers and the sum of them will be calculated. This sum will be used to generate a random number from 0 to 100 for the love percentage.
